name: Empathy Map Template
description:
Hey Designer.

A clean and easy to use template for quickly generating User Empathy Maps when working on your UX Project created by Ashish for DopeUX.


👉🏽 Symbols

👉🏽 Named Layers

👉🏽 Clean Design


Feel free and Duplicate it and don't forget to press "❤️". Thank you 🙌🏻
